# Ceal AI Product Context

- Build for boutique creative agencies closing $5k-$20k projects.
- Optimize the final handoff experience to reduce "zombie project" delays.
- Protect the two key moments:
  1) "Aha moment" from SOW upload to AI-generated checklist.
  2) "Certified closing" client sign-off with confidence.
- Keep AI human-supervised: AI proposes deliverables, agency approves before client-facing changes.
- Every major feature should reinforce one of these:
  - Faster time-to-close
  - Fewer missing-asset disputes
  - Better professional trust at handoff
